author: wn.com
title: Joint Chiefs of Staff chairman arrives in Iraq for update on fight against ISIS
text: The top U.S. military officer landed in Iraq Tuesday to get an update on the battle against ISIS militants, saying he sees no prospect right now for Russia to expand its airstrike campaign into the war-torn country. ...
